description: The MSCI USA Consumer Staples Net Total Return USD Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid cap companies from USA part of the Consumer Staples sector as classified by GICS Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Reviewed on a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI USA Consumer Staples UCITS ETF 1D
